  "description": "The workhorse lead. Full harmonic series, strong fundamental, high sync but not total — there is still life in the partials. Duende is the raw emotional power in flamenco singing. Velocity shapes both brightness and effort — soft keys whisper, hard keys belt. The preset that proves the engine can simply be played.",
